   "width": 1677.11,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "The Edge Agent polls the server outbound, so only TCP 8000 and 9443 need to cross from the VLAN 80 server zone to 192.168.40.35. Once online, its container list mirrors `docker ps` on the host, and a restart keeps the same environment without a duplicate record.",
   "originalText": "The Edge Agent polls the server outbound, so only TCP 8000 and 9443 need to cross from the VLAN 80 server zone to 192.168.40.35. Once online, its container list mirrors `docker ps` on the host, and a restart keeps the same environment without a duplicate record.",
